de.team33.libs.exceptional.v3

Class Wrapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.team33.libs.exceptional.v3.Wrapping

  • public final class Wrapping
extends Object
    A utility that can turn certain functional constructs that may throw several, or unspecific, checked exceptions into others that wraps such exceptions as RuntimeEnvelope or CheckedEnvelope.
